text.section:
Each Fund consists of:
money allocated to the Fund for the respective county in the annual budgets of the Commission under Subtitle 1 of this title;
proceeds of bonds issued under this section and allocated to the Fund;
investment earnings of the Fund; and
any other money from any other source accepted for the benefit of the Fund.

section.section:
At any time after acquiring land, on repayment to the Commission of the amount disbursed by the Commission for the land plus interest, the Commission may transfer the land to:
a construction agency of the State;
Montgomery County;
Prince George's County;
the redevelopment authority of Prince George's County;
the revenue authority of Prince George's County; or
a municipal corporation or governed special taxing district in Montgomery County or Prince George's County.
